<td class=article width=420>
<a href="/web/20050414054430/http://us.rd.yahoo.com/dailynews/ap/brand/SIG=br2v03/*http://www.ap.org">
<img src="/web/20050414054430im_/http://us.i1.yimg.com/us.yimg.com/i/us/nws/p/ap120a.gif" border=0 alt="AP" width=120 align=right height=31></a>
<div class=storyheadline>Rudolph Pleads Guilty in Olympic Bombing
</div>
<br clear=all>
<table width=420 border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0>
<tr valign=middle>
<td width=40%>
<!-- Yahoo TimeStamp: 1113453648 -->
                   <!-- recent_timestamp 1113453648 3834 secs not stale 28800 secs -->
 <div class=recenttimedate>1 hour,  3 minutes ago</div>
</td>
<td align=right nowrap width=60%>
<table width=1% cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 border=0>
<tr><td width=1%><a href="/web/20050414054430/http://us.rd.yahoo.com/dailynews/addtomy/*http://add.my.yahoo.com/content?id=6063&amp;.src=yn&amp;.done=http%3a//news.yahoo.com/news%3ftmpl=story%26e=1%26u=/ap/20050414/ap_on_re_us/eric_rudolph%26sid=84439559"><img src=/web/20050414054430im_/http://us.i1.yimg.com/us.yimg.com/i/us/my/addtomyyahoo3.gif width=62 height=17 border=0 align=absmiddle alt="Add to My Yahoo!"></a></td><td nowrap width=99%>&nbsp;<span class=regs><a href="/web/20050414054430/http://us.rd.yahoo.com/dailynews/addtomy/*http://add.my.yahoo.com/content?id=6063&amp;.src=yn&amp;.done=http%3a//news.yahoo.com/news%3ftmpl=story%26e=1%26u=/ap/20050414/ap_on_re_us/eric_rudolph%26sid=84439559">U.S. National - AP</a></span></td></tr></table>
</td>
</tr></table>
<p>
<!-- TextStart -->
<font size=-1><i>By KRISTEN WYATT, Associated Press Writer</i></font>
<p>
ATLANTA - 
<font face=arial size=-1>
A defiant Eric Rudolph pleaded guilty Wednesday to carrying out the deadly bombing at the 1996 Atlanta Olympics and three other attacks, saying he picked the Summer Games to embarrass the U.S. government in front of the world "for its abominable sanctioning of abortion on demand."
</font>
<p>
<table width="1%" cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0 align=left>
    <tr valign=top>
    <td width=99%>
 
<!-- ult -->
    <center>
 <table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=150>
 <tr valign=top>
 <td>
<center>
 <a href="/web/20050414054430/http://story.news.yahoo.com/news?tmpl=story&amp;u=/050413/480/aljb10204131343"><img
 src="/web/20050414054430im_/http://us.news1.yimg.com/us.yimg.com/p/ap/20050413/thumb.aljb10204131343.eric_rudolph_us_bombing_suspect_aljb102.jpg" width=130 height=90 border=1 alt="Photo"></a><br><a href="/web/20050414054430/http://story.news.yahoo.com/news?tmpl=story&amp;u=/050413/480/aljb10204131343" class=regs>AP Photo</a>
</center><br>
<!-- /web/20050414054430/http://us.news1.yimg.com/us.yimg.com/p/ap/20050414/thumb.aljr60104140231.al_eric_rudolph_witness_aljr601.jpg && (/web/20050414054430/http://us.news1.yimg.com/us.yimg.com/p/ap/20050414/thumb.aljr60104140231.al_eric_rudolph_witness_aljr601.jpg ~~ "http") -->
 <!-- SlideshowStart -->
